      "snippet": "### Credentials & Configuration - **Airtable API Token:** patxbDkv88pOMXmYx.c7e5fd7974954e3a674087090835d11dd69504f3912f0ef86c3c59f1e91febdd - **Airtable Base:** \"Curbin\" (apptYNRJTXwItvied) - **ServiceStops Table:** tbl7r5OBk0L7Epnro - **Google Maps API:** AIzaSyCzfj1D1eF01IDHwCMGqt4O4XU1ncouSRI - **Server:** PHP 8.3.30, Apache 2.4, cURL enabled ### Architecture Decisions - **PHP over Node.js** — Hostinger shared hosting limitation - **Embedded credentials** — Simpler for shared hosting (no .env support) - **Haversine distance** — Local calculation, no API cost - **CORS via .htaccess** — Works on all Apache versions - **localStorage** — Worker name persistence across sessions ### Document",
