      "snippet": "2. **Wire real Telegram approval pings** — currently placeholder `REPLACE_WITH_TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` in `mission-control/api/config.php`. Chat ID `8714809782`. 3. **Battle-test Quick Fix patch flow** end-to-end after recovery. 4. **Proper Iterate flow** — currently loop-back on Reject is manual. Should automate Builder re-trigger with rejection feedback. 5. **Auto-deploy after LAST enabled audit stage** — verify firing logic, not just after Builder. ## Credentials (operational, not secret-level) - MC password: `MissionControl2026!` - Auth: POST `/api/auth.php` `{\"password\":\"...\"}` → PHPSESSID cookie - Runner heartbeat secret: `mc-runner-heartbeat-2026` - Airtable token + Anthropic key: see ME",
