      "snippet": "### Browser Cache Disabled **Implementation:** - Added meta tags to index.html (Cache-Control, Pragma, Expires) - Created `.htaccess` file with server-side cache prevention - Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate - Pragma: no-cache - Expires: 0 - ETags disabled - Applies to: HTML, JS, CSS, images, fonts, PHP **Result:** Browser will never cache any files; visitors always see latest version **Status:** ✅ Deployed (commit 97d5062) ### Navigation Bar Complete Rebuild — index2.html **Approach:** Used Claude Opus to rebuild nav from scratch (vs. transform hacks) **Removed:** - ❌ transform:scale() hacks (0.5, 1.3, 1.8) - ❌ Safari @supports overrides - ❌ Invalid CSS (or combin",
