      "snippet": "4. ✅ **Discovered the built-in `openrouter` plugin** at `/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/extensions/openrouter/` 5. ✅ Removed all manual config, enabled the plugin + set `OPENROUTER_API_KEY` env var 6. ✅ Plugin auto-resolved `openrouter/moonshotai/kimi-k2.7-code` dynamically. Switch worked. ### Gateway hang (real outage) During the OpenRouter wiring, multiple back-to-back SIGUSR1 restarts left the gateway stuck. I went silent for several minutes. Chris recovered me via: 1. Hostinger panel → container shell 2. `openclaw doctor` 3. Manual `openclaw gateway restart` Then I came back online on Kimi K2.7 Code as the active model. ### Notable observations - OpenRouter free tier is es",
